  "title": "Legal Secretaries",
  "description": "<p>Lee & Lee LLP invites applications for Legal Secretaries to join our Real Estate and Property Department.<br /><br />Candidates should:</p><ol><li>Be experienced in the preparation of conveyancing documents and legal completions;</li><li>Be familiar with the usual word processing programs, e.g. Word, Excel and Power Point;</li><li>Be competent with searches and lodgements;</li><li>Expected with searches and lodgements;</li><li>Expected to work with more than one Lawyer;</li><li>Be a team player and also able to work independently.</li></ol><p>Please send your detailed resume and academic results to hr@leenlee.com.sg with a recent photograph, current and expected salary.<br /></p><p></p>",
